 justify-center rounded-xl transition-transform duration-normal group-hover:scale-110\" style=\"background-color:#3a6b4a15;color:#3a6b4a\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shopping-cart\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"21\" r=\"1\"></circle><circle cx=\"19\" cy=\"21\" r=\"1\"></circle><path d=\"M2.05 2.05h2l2.66 12.42a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.58h9.78a2 2 0 0 0 1.95-1.57l1.65-7.43H5.12\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-1 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Meal Prep &amp; Compras</h3><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]\">0<!-- --> negocios · <!-- -->0<!-- -->% sin web</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--primary)] opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-normal group-hover:opacity-100\">Ver plantilla <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"mt-3 h-1 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-[var(--border)]\"><div class=\"h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-slow\" style=\"width:0%;background-color:#3a6b4a\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"proyectos\" class=\"scroll-mt-20 py-20 md:py-28\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"section-fade mx-auto mb-14 max-w-2xl text-center\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--primary)]\">Ejemplos</p><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)] sm:text-4xl\">Ejemplos de Sitios</h2><p class=\"text-[var(--text-light)]\">Estos son ejemplos demo generados con nuestra plataforma. Te muestran como luce un sitio real para cada tipo de negocio.</p></div><div class=\"section-fade grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"></div><div class=\"section-fade mt-10 text-center\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[var(--primary)]\" href=\"/admin\">Ver mas ejemplos en el panel admin <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section id=\"como-funciona\" class=\"scroll-mt-20 bg-[var(--surface-light)] py-20 md:py-28\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-5xl\"><div class=\"section-fade mx-auto mb-14 max-w-2xl text-center\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--primary)]\">Como Funciona</p><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)] sm:text-4xl\">Tu sitio web en 3 pasos</h2></div><div class=\"section-fade grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mb-5 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--primary)]\">01</div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Selecciona tu tipo de negocio</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Elegi entre nuestras plantillas iniciales o pedi una generacion IA adaptada a tu rubro.</p></div><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mb-5 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--primary)]\">02</div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Completa tus datos</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Nombre, servicios, precios, horarios, equipo — todo lo que tu negocio necesita.</p></div><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mb-5 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--primary)]\">03</div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Tu sitio esta listo</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]\">En minutos tenes un sitio web profesional, optimizado y listo para recibir clientes.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"funcionalidades\" class=\"scroll-mt-20 py-20 md:py-28\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"section-fade mx-auto mb-14 max-w-2xl text-center\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--primary)]\">Funcionalidades</p><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)] sm:text-4xl\">Todo lo que tu negocio necesita</h2><p class=\"text-[var(--text-light)]\">Cada sitio incluye funcionalidades profesionales pensadas para maximizar la visibilidad y conversion de tu negocio.</p></div><div class=\"section-fade grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wand-sparkles\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.64 3.64-1.28-1.28a1.21 1.21 0 0 0-1.72 0L2.36 18.64a1.21 1.21 0 0 0 0 1.72l1.28 1.28a1.2 1.2 0 0 0 1.72 0L21.64 5.36a1.2 1.2 0 0 0 0-1.72\"></path><path d=\"m14 7 3 3\"></path><path d=\"M5 6v4\"></path><path d=\"M19 14v4\"></path><path d=\"M10 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M7 8H3\"></path><path d=\"M21 16h-4\"></path><path d=\"M11 3H9\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Generacion con IA</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Contenido, diseno y SEO generados automaticamente para cada tipo de negocio.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-smartphone\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"20\" x=\"5\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">100% Responsive</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Sitios optimizados para movil, tablet y desktop desde el primer momento.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">SEO Integrado</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Meta tags, Schema.org y contenido optimizado para posicionar en Google.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">WhatsApp Directo</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Boton flotante de WhatsApp para que tus clientes te contacten al instante.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Dominio Propio</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Cada negocio con su propia URL profesional y certificado SSL.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layers\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12.83 2.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 6.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.83l8.58 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0l8.58-3.9a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.83z\"></path><path d=\"M2 12a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 12\"></path><path d=\"M2 17a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 17\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">13 Plantillas</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Disenos especializados para multiples tipos de negocio: belleza, bienestar, diseno, meal prep, reubicacion y mas.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-[var(--surface-light)] py-20 md:py-28\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-5xl\"><div class=\"section-fade mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--primary)]\">Oportunidad de Mercado</p><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)] sm:text-4xl\">Paraguay necesita presencia digital</h2><p class=\"mb-12 text-[var(--text-light)]\">Nuestro analisis de mercado en el sector belleza y bienestar en Paraguay revela una oportunidad masiva: la mayoria aun no tiene presencia web. El patron se repite en otros rubros.</p></div><div class=\"section-fade grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 text-center transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-3 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)]\">+7,400</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text)]\">Negocios Identificados</p><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\">En todo Paraguay</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 text-center transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-3 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)]\">75%</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text)]\">Sin Sitio Web</p><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\">+5,600 negocios</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 text-center transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-3 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)]\">+3,900</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text)]\">Leads Prioritarios</p><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Priority A (con telefono, sin web)</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-6 text-center transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-3 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)]/10 text-[var(--primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text)]\">209</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text)]\">Ciudades Cubiertas</p><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Con oportunidades identificadas</p></div></div><p class=\"section-fade mt-8 text-center text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Datos de nuestro analisis de mercado (abril 2026, Google Maps Places API, sector belleza y bienestar).</p></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-28\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--primary)] to-[var(--primary)]\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-10\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 h-96 w-96 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-white blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"absolute right-0 bottom-0 h-96 w-96 translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-white blur-3xl\"></div></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-5xl\"><div class=\"section-fade mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center\"><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--primary-foreground)] sm:text-4xl\">Lleva tu negocio al mundo digital</h2><p class=\"mb-8 text-lg text-[var(--primary-foreground)]/80\">Unite a los negocios paraguayos que estan listos para crecer con una presencia web profesional, rapida y pensada para convertir.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-white px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--primary)] shadow-button transition-all duration-normal hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-card-hover\" href=\"/admin\">Comenzar Ahora<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#plantillas\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border-2 border-white/30 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-normal hover:border-white/60\">Explorar Plantillas</a></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"border-t border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] py-12\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><div class=\"mb-3 flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--primary)] text-[var(--primary-foreground)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" f